ABOUT
     DSBBatmon is a Qt battery monitor for FreeBSD. It displays the battery's
     current status, capacity, and remaining time when you move the mouse
     cursor over its tray icon. Clicking on the tray icon brings up/hides the
     settings window. DSBBatmon can automatically shut down or suspend your
     system if the battery's capacity falls short of a certain percental value.

INSTALLATION
     # git clone https://github.com/mrclksr/dsbbatmon.git
     # cd dsbbatmon && qmake && make && make install

